                        <item xml:id="a3_5243">
                           <locus target="#59r-59v">-59r-59v</locus>
                           <q xml:lang="en">Ministry of Public Health / Malaria Eradication Service / House Visit Card.
House No. 125 ; Locality No. 289 ; Name of sector Agaro ; Name of zone Jimma ; Name of head of family Haji Momamed Seid ; Number in the family (including head of family) 6.
Date / Name &amp; Signature of MES Visitors / Title / Action Taken</q>
                           <q xml:lang="am"/>
                           <desc>Loose folio</desc>
                           <note>Bilingual form in Amharic and English. In the top left, portrait of Emperor Haile Selassie. The form is filled in English. The dates of visits extend from 28/10/64 to 5/11/71. 
